title: Two to tango
description: It takes two to Tango is a combination of an oak sculpture 1.80 meters high and a serpentine sculpture of approximately 250x10x5 cm.
context:
It takes two to Tango is a combination of an oak sculpture 1.80 meters high and a serpentine sculpture of approximately 250x10x5 cm. The sculpture stands on an oval of dark natural stone

The sculpture shows a dancing couple performing the tango. The back is sleek and stylistic, the front has a realistic, playful perspective.
